James and I are going to carry on with ping
pong. Now I'm rubbish at ping pong. James

00:00:11.550 --> 00:00:16.280
is much better than me. But this gets much
trickier when you take gravity away, so let's

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:19.270
have a look at that.

00:00:19.270 --> 00:00:31.630
