quite a lot of ping pong balls for this because

00:00:31.630 --> 00:00:35.350
I kept losing them, and you keep losing them
because you're floating. The balls are floating,

00:00:35.350 --> 00:00:39.360
and they just don't do what they do do on
Earth. I'm not entirely sure--

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:43.390
[LAUGHTER]

00:00:43.390 --> 00:00:45.660
I have no idea, OK?

00:00:45.660 --> 00:00:46.660
[LAUGHTER]

00:00:46.660 --> 00:00:49.870
So the ball doesn't behave like this. The
laws of physics are the same, but the physics

00:00:49.870 --> 00:00:54.050
of your situation have changed, so everything
is more difficult. Alex, shall we have a quick

00:00:54.050 --> 00:00:56.070
game? Yeah?

00:00:56.070 --> 00:00:59.100
